OL,3,CJohn Lewis Partnership to hire 12,500
OL,4,Cworkers for festive period
OL,6,FThe John Lewis Partnership (JLP) is to
OL,7,Fhire 12,500 temporary staff in its
OL,8,Fbiggest ever recruitment drive for the
OL,9,Ffestive period.
OL,11,FThe retail group said it will hire
OL,12,Fstaff across its John Lewis department
OL,13,Fstore business and Waitrose grocery
OL,14,Farm.
OL,16,FJLP said the firm will hire 4,100 more
OL,17,Ftemporary workers than in the same
OL,18,Fperiod last year.
