OL,3,CJohn Lewis Partnership to hire 12,500
OL,4,Cworkers for festive period
OL,6,FThe roles will be in Waitrose and John
OL,7,FLewis shops and across the group's
OL,8,Fdistribution network to support it
OL,9,Faround its busiest period, in the run-
OL,10,Fup to Black Friday, Christmas and John
OL,11,FLewis's sale period in January.
OL,13,FWaitrose is to start recruiting 7,700
OL,14,Fseasonal roles across more than 300
OL,15,Fshops in the coming weeks, including
OL,16,Fsupermarket assistants, night shift
OL,17,Fworkers and customer delivery drivers.
OL,19,FRecruitment for 2,000 temporary roles
OL,20,Fat the 34 John Lewis stores is already
OL,21,Funder way.
