OL,4,Cworkers for festive period
OL,6,FThe retailer said it has a "small
OL,7,Fnumber" of vacancies remaining after a
OL,8,Fhigh level of interest.
OL,10,FThe partnership is also recruiting
OL,11,Faround 2,800 workers in its supply
OL,12,Fchain through agencies for roles such
OL,13,Fas warehouse workers and drivers to
OL,14,Fdeal with increased online demand.
OL,16,FIt said it has already witnessed
OL,17,Fstrong demand for Christmas products
OL,18,Fin recent weeks, with volumes of its
OL,19,FWaitrose Christmas range up 25% year-
OL,20,Fon-year and sales of decorations from
OL,21,Fits John Lewis Christmas shop up 20%.
