OL,6,FCharlotte Lock, customer director at
OL,7,FJLP, said: "Whether making sure you're
OL,8,Fchoosing the right headphones or
OL,9,Fwanting inspirational food ideas for
OL,10,Fentertaining, we know customers value
OL,11,Fthe independent, trusted advice they
OL,12,Fget from our partners and that
OL,13,Ffriendly, personal touch.
OL,15,F"Our partners have always been at the
OL,16,Fheart of what sets us apart ` we're
OL,17,Fthrilled by the interest the roles
OL,18,Fhave already received and that people
OL,19,Fwant to be part of the excitement that
OL,20,Fsurrounds our two brands at Christmas."
